trans-title=Greece acquires 2 types of Switchblade roving ammunition: their capabilities and the new obstacle for Turkey in the Aegean and Thrace |url=https://nemesishd.gr/news/greece-switchblade-300-600-approve-egkrisi-loitering-munition/ |access-date=2024-09-19 |website=NEMESIS HD |language=el}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |date=2024-09-14 |title=Mini drone procurement on the cards |url=https://www.ekathimerini.com/politics/foreign-policy/1248403/mini-drone-procurement-on-the-cards/ |access-date=2024-09-19 |website=ekathimerini.com |language=English}}</ref>

